    "description": "Exo Rally Championship 是银河系最危险的越野赛事活动。欢迎来到赛车的终极前线——地处偏远、未经勘探、极富异世界感的拉力赛。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262020/extras/6b0633cc4168151a1cbb55d4832ec0fc.poster.avif?t=1766360166\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262020/extras/6b0633cc4168151a1cbb55d4832ec0fc.webm?t=1766360166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262020/extras/6b0633cc4168151a1cbb55d4832ec0fc.mp4?t=1766360166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>掌舵先进的 RCS 推进器增强型漫游者，操纵异常逼真的竞速模拟。您可以征服棘手荒凉的外星地貌；在程序生成的各个阶段中，处处都是会破坏硬件的恶劣天气和地形挑战，您却在各个路径点间加速前行。投入到受地球传奇拉力赛启发的职业模式中去，并对您的漫游者进行定制、微调和修整，优化它的性能，直面多种多样的环境。应对银河系最激烈的越野拉力赛事，突破速度与控制的界限。<br><br>开启一段从失败者到夺冠者的旅程，不断晋级，挑战最厉害的车队，争夺至高无上的 Exo Rally Championship 头衔。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262020/extras/dbe16315e5a7547ac8714d93abc7acfb.poster.avif?t=1766360166\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262020/extras/dbe16315e5a7547ac8714d93abc7acfb.webm?t=1766360166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262020/extras/dbe16315e5a7547ac8714d93abc7acfb.mp4?t=1766360166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>未经开发的荒芜星球，恶劣的天气，会使硬件遭受损坏的极端气温和暴风，超自然的地形构成，以及目之所及无路可走<br></li><li>硬核的越野物理模拟器，逼真的轮胎模型，动力传动系统，悬架和损耗<br></li><li>耗燃有限的 RCS 式推进器，可实现跳跃、着陆、空中控制和更多性能，有助于管理危机四伏、“真正越野”的环境<br></li><li>程序生成的各种行星和阶段，意味着每一关都决不重复<br></li><li>基于现实世界的拉力赛、Baja 和达喀尔拉力赛等活动的丰富职业模式<br></li><li>与各支车队竞速，不断进步，从后进者中奋勇崛起，与佼佼者竞争，争夺 Exo Rally Championship 头衔<br></li><li>深度管理系统，能让您对自己的漫游者进行定制、微调和修整<br></li><li>与好友分享种子，以生成相同的阶段，竞争最佳成绩</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262020/extras/970d62d1ef4c3ebbb5c7d687f9d4bc27.poster.avif?t=1766360166\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262020/extras/970d62d1ef4c3ebbb5c7d687f9d4bc27.webm?t=1766360166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262020/extras/970d62d1ef4c3ebbb5c7d687f9d4bc27.mp4?t=1766360166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
